description: Luck Dish shares the good luck of Japanese Curry with the streets of Los Angeles. Focusing on the healing powers of curry and taking care to provide all natural ingredients in the dishes, Luck Dish has some of the most amazing Curry roaming LA. Luck Dish fuses Japanese Chicken Curry with street dish favorites like curry Burritos, Nachos, Quesadillas, and Tacos. Choose your spice level from 1 to 5 (5 is the HOTTEST!), and enjoy Luck Dish!
name: LuckDish Curry
